metadata.name: Together
metadata.description:
Roses shaping the atmosphere, symbolizing and giving off intense love. It is because they're together, that the flowers bring such fierce feelings into the mix!

From collection Stellar  
"Stellar" is a collection about never-ending human love & its infinite reaches, transcending even space and time. An encapsulation of "love" being just as intense even on a far-away planet â€” is it what defines us as humans? Or is it what gives us purpose as humans?
